# TOR Configuration for Tor Anonymizer
SOCKSPort 9050
ControlPort 9051
DataDirectory ./tor_data
Log notice file ./logs/tor.log

# Security settings
SafeLogging 1
SafeSocks 1
TestSocks 1

# Performance
AvoidDiskWrites 1

# Circuit settings
MaxCircuitDirtiness 600
NewCircuitPeriod 300
MaxClientCircuitsPending 32

# Exit policies (restrictive)
ExitPolicy reject *:*
ExitPolicy reject6 *:*

# DNS
ClientUseIPv6 0
